high_descs: Take the blue plate on the left out of the fridge.
Turn around and bring the plate to the the microwave above the stove.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Bring the heated plate down to the cabinet on the right in the corner.
Put the heated plate in the corner cabinet on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate down in a corner cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room to the black fridge.
Open the fridge door, pick up the blue plate on the left on the second shelf and close the door.
Turn around and cross the room to the white stove on your left.
Place the blue plate inside the microwave, heat it up for three seconds, and remove the blue plate from the microwave.
Turn right and open the lower cabinet to the far left.
Place the blue plate inside the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate in a cabinet.

high_descs: cross the room to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, remove the blue container on the left, and close the refrigerator door
open the microwave, insert the blue container into the microwave, and turn on the microwave for 4 seconds. Then open the microwave, remove the container, and close the microwave door
look down, turn right, and advance a short distance to the cabinets in front of you
open the cabinet, place the blue container in the cabinet, and then close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: place a slightly heated blue container from the refrigerator into a cabinet
